headline: UDR, Inc. Announces Executive Management Promotions and Leadership Transition Plans
summary: DENVER, January 02, 2025--UDR, Inc. (the "Company") (NYSE: UDR), a leading multifamily real estate investment trust, today announced the following Executive Management promotions and Leadership Transition plans effective January 1, 2025.
